\par\plain {The Atlantic was feeding a hurricane so the beach line all the way out to the break is solid white with foam and I am right to fear it but I hop right in and paddle out anyways but fuck me my arms are noodles inside ten minutes and my icy fingers can hardly hang onto my board through a duck dive and fuck my brothers wetsuit for being too tight in the shoulders and my whole mouth for going so numb that I can hardly move my lips and why is it always me that gets this headache that comes on way too fast even though I grow out my hair for the insulation god I can feel the cold water pulling the heat straight out of my crown which was the second of ten ways I might die with the fifth being the violence of the break that I am actively paddling towards like a madman offering himself to Neptune or Yahweh or whatever protected indian burial mound peaked the dunes and demanded that I cower in spray of these deep green slabs as they tower up to comb over and crash my god I am Saul on the road to Damascus because there is power in the water here which changes the sense of what I am and what the world is.}}